---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Cookie Policy — AI Zest"
  description="AI Zest cookie policy — how we use cookies and similar tracking technologies on our website."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#3B82F6]">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium">Cookie Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-10">Last updated: June 23, 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">1. What Are Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work efficiently and provide information to the site owners.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        AI Zest uses cookies for the following purposes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Essential Cookies</strong> — required for the basic functionality of the Site (e.g., dark mode preference)</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics Cookies</strong> — to understand how visitors interact with our Site and improve user experience</li>
        <li><strong>Affiliate Cookies</strong> — when you click an affiliate link, a cookie may be placed to track referrals for commission purposes (e.g., via Awin)</li>
        <li><strong>Email Service Cookies</strong> — MailerLite may place cookies to manage newsletter signup forms</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Cookie Type</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Purpose</th>
              <th class="text-left py-2 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Duration</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">dark-mode</td>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Stores your dark/light mode preference</td>
              <td class="py-2">Session / Persistent</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Awin affiliate cookies</td>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Tracks affiliate referrals from Awin links</td>
              <td class="py-2">30 days (typical)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">MailerLite cookies</td>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Manages newsletter signup interactions</td>
              <td class="py-2">As set by MailerLite</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Cloudflare cookies</td>
              <td class="py-2 pr-4">Security and performance optimization</td>
              <td class="py-2">Session</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Some cookies are placed by third-party services that appear on our Site:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1 mt-2">
        <li><strong>MailerLite</strong> — email newsletter platform (<a href="https://www.mailerlite.com/legal/cookie-policy" class="text-[#3B82F6] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MailerLite Cookie Policy</a>)</li>
        <li><strong>Awin</strong> — affiliate network (<a href="https://www.awin.com/gb/legal" class="text-[#3B82F6] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Awin Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — CDN and security (<a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-[#3B82F6] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">5. Managing Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Most web browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings → Privacy and Security → Cookies and other site data</li>
        <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Options → Privacy & Security → Cookies and Site Data</li>
        <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences → Privacy → Cookies and website data</li>
        <li><strong>Edge:</strong> Settings → Cookies and site permissions → Cookies</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
        Please note that disabling cookies may affect the functionality of our Site, including affiliate link tracking.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">6. Updates</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. Changes are effective immediately upon posting. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        If you have any questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at:
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#3B82F6] mt-2">
        <a href="mailto:admin@aizest.net" class="hover:underline">admin@aizest.net</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
